title: Aalatettix
text:
Aalatettix is a genus of groundhopper, in the family <a href="Tetrigidae">Tetrigidae</a>, with species found in southern China (including Hainan island).
The <a href="type%20species">type species</a>, identified in 2002, of this genus is known as Aalatettix longipulvillus. Later more species where identified as belonging to this genus.
